------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Layer Window Mootools plugin
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a window layer class designed with mootools.
The window is opened as a layer above the document. Can be dragged and resized.
His content may be a DOM Element html content, a passed string or a ajax request
response.

This class uses the ajaxRequest function provided in ajax.js file.
 
REQUIREMENTS
Mootools core >= 1.2
Mootools more Drag plugin
